        android:text="Step 2:  Put in the cornflower and a splash of milk into the bowl which is used to cook the cauliflower and mix that into a smooth paste.
Add the rest of the milk and then season the paste. Then add in the mustard, cheedar and the thyme and stir it together.
Then add the cauliflower. Add the butter on top and microwave for approx 5 minutes until tender and cheese has melted. Leave to cool and then grill until golden. "
